0. vimscripts refine 
1. SearchBar : to find all definition of all source file in a predefine-folder(or current-folder). 
2. HighLight : current word in current buffer by <shift + F8> with custom highlight color.

3. Terminal : invoke a terminal window.
4. Preview_File_Window: preview window if current cursor located word is a file_name & the file exist.

5. ctrl + <- / -> : to select ---> then copy or delete.(vistual mode)

5. auto-complete : member_complete or prefix-string_complete
6. Tag : add current line to tag, jump back.(reason: when using '#' or ':/', cursor will be auto-located and can't jump back)
7. BUGFIX : multi window | the ctags file not in current path
